---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Copyright Notice | WinFlowz";
---

<MainLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  lang="en"
  structuredData={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "@id": "https://winflowz.com/copyright",
    "url": "https://winflowz.com/copyright",
    "name": "Copyright Notice | WinFlowz",
    "description": "Copyright and intellectual property rights notice for WinFlowz digital productivity tools and services.",
    "inLanguage": "en"
  }}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Copyright Notice</h1>

    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Last updated: December 15, 2024</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">1. Copyright Protection</h2>
      <p>
        All content, software, and materials available on this website and associated products (collectively, the "Content") are protected by intellectual property laws and are the property of WinFlowz. This includes, but is not limited to:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>All Obsidian plugins (CreatorFlowz, RSSFlowz, PluginFlowz, MediaFlowz, EditorFlowz, MailingFlowz, LinkFlowz)</li>
        <li>Chrome extensions (TubeFlowz)</li>
        <li>Training materials and documentation</li>
        <li>Source code and algorithms</li>
        <li>User interface designs and graphics</li>
        <li>Website content and structure</li>
        <li>Brand names, logos, and trademarks</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Copyright Protection:</strong> The Content is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. Any unauthorized use, reproduction, modification, distribution, transmission, republication, display, or performance of the Content is strictly prohibited.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">License Restrictions:</strong> Purchase of our products grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license for personal use only. This license explicitly prohibits:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Copying, modifying, or creating derivative works</li>
        <li>Reverse engineering or decompiling our software</li>
        <li>Redistributing or reselling our products</li>
        <li>Removing copyright notices or product identifications</li>
        <li>Using our code in other products or services</li>
        <li>Sharing access credentials or license keys</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Commercial Use:</strong> Any commercial use, including but not limited to resale, modification, or incorporation into other products, requires explicit written permission from WinFlowz.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Enforcement:</strong> We actively monitor for copyright infringement and will take appropriate legal action to protect our intellectual property rights, including:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Issuing cease and desist notices</li>
        <li>Pursuing damages for copyright infringement</li>
        <li>Reporting violations to relevant platforms and authorities</li>
        <li>Seeking injunctive relief</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Fair Use:</strong> Limited use of our Content may be permitted for review, commentary, or educational purposes, subject to proper attribution and respect for our intellectual property rights.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Reporting Violations:</strong> If you discover any unauthorized use or distribution of our Content, please report it to copyright@winflowz.com. Include relevant details and evidence to help us investigate the matter.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8">
        By using our products and services, you acknowledge and agree to respect our intellectual property rights as outlined in this notice. WinFlowz reserves all rights not expressly granted and may update this notice at any time without prior notification.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">For copyright inquiries or permissions, please contact copyright@winflowz.com</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
